       <li><p style="text-align: center;"> &nbsp;</p> <p style="font-family: 'Microsoft Yahei'; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 13px; text-align: center;"> <span style="line-height: 33px; font-size: 22px;"><span style="line-height: 21px;"><span style="line-height: 24px;">网络特警硬件监控设备的架构优势</span></span></span><br /> &nbsp;</p> <p style="font-family: 'Microsoft Yahei'; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center;"> <font color="#333333" size="3"><span style="line-height: 24px;">国内架构最先进、最稳定、监控效率最高的局域网上网行为控制系统</span></font></p> 
        <hr /> <br /> 
